{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "hermes-agent", "elements": [{"type": "text", "id": "title", "x": 200, "y": 10, "text": "Epistemic Probing Results\nQwen3.5-4B — 656 Questions", "fontSize": 32, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#e9ecef", "originalText": "Epistemic Probing Results\nQwen3.5-4B — 656 Questions", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "subtitle", "x": 200, "y": 80, "text": "Can we predict if an LLM will be right or wrong BEFORE it answers?", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "originalText": "Can we predict if an LLM will be right or wrong BEFORE it answers?", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "s1_bg", "x": 20, "y": 120, "width": 280, "height": 340, "backgroundColor": "#1a1a2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "strokeWidth": 2, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "opacity": 80}, {"type": "text", "id": "s1_title", "x": 30, "y": 130, "text": "THE MODEL", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "originalText": "THE MODEL", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s1_desc", "x": 30, "y": 155, "text": "Qwen3.5-4B\n32 layers, 2560-dim\nBase model (not RLHF'd)", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#ced4da", "originalText": "Qwen3.5-4B\n32 layers, 2560-dim\nBase model (not RLHF'd)", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "lyr5", "x": 60, "y": 200, "width": 40, "height": 18, "backgroundColor": "#364fc7", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "lyr5_t", "x": 110, "y": 200, "text": "Layer 5  AUROC 0.74", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#868e96", "originalText": "Layer 5  AUROC 0.74", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "lyr10", "x": 60, "y": 225, "width": 40, "height": 18, "backgroundColor": "#364fc7", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "lyr10_t", "x": 110, "y": 225, "text": "Layer 10  AUROC 0.76", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#868e96", "originalText": "Layer 10  AUROC 0.76", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "lyr15", "x": 60, "y": 250, "width": 40, "height": 18, "backgroundColor": "#364fc7", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "lyr15_t", "x": 110, "y": 250, "text": "Layer 15  AUROC 0.80", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#868e96", "originalText": "Layer 15  AUROC 0.80", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "lyr20", "x": 60, "y": 275, "width": 40, "height": 18, "backgroundColor": "#3b5bdb", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "lyr20_t", "x": 110, "y": 275, "text": "Layer 20  AUROC 0.88", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "originalText": "Layer 20  AUROC 0.88", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "lyr25", "x": 60, "y": 300, "width": 40, "height": 18, "backgroundColor": "#4c6ef5", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "lyr25_t", "x": 110, "y": 300, "text": "Layer 25  AUROC 0.88 ★", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#e9ecef", "originalText": "Layer 25  AUROC 0.88 ★", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "lyr30", "x": 60, "y": 325, "width": 40, "height": 18, "backgroundColor": "#5c7cfa", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "lyr30_t", "x": 110, "y": 325, "text": "Layer 30  AUROC 0.90 ★ BEST", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#ffd43b", "originalText": "Layer 30  AUROC 0.90 ★ BEST", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "lyr31", "x": 60, "y": 350, "width": 40, "height": 18, "backgroundColor": "#748ffc", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "lyr31_t", "x": 110, "y": 350, "text": "Layer 31  AUROC 0.89", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "originalText": "Layer 31  AUROC 0.89", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s1_arrow", "x": 30, "y": 385, "text": "← Signal grows with depth →", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#4263eb", "originalText": "← Signal grows with depth →", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "s2_bg", "x": 330, "y": 120, "width": 320, "height": 340, "backgroundColor": "#1a1a2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#2b8a3e", "strokeWidth": 2, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "opacity": 80}, {"type": "text", "id": "s2_title", "x": 340, "y": 130, "text": "WHAT WORKS ✅", "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#40c057", "originalText": "WHAT WORKS ✅", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s2_body", "x": 340, "y": 165, "text": "Factual QA (MMLU)\n\nAUROC: 0.65 → 0.87\nacross layers 5 to 31\n\nTraining-free probe:\n0.78 → 0.88\n(zero parameters!)\n\nThe model KNOWS when\nit's about to be wrong —\nBEFORE it says anything.", "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#b2f2bb", "originalText": "Factual QA (MMLU)\n\nAUROC: 0.65 → 0.87\nacross layers 5 to 31\n\nTraining-free probe:\n0.78 → 0.88\n(zero parameters!)\n\nThe model KNOWS when\nit's about to be wrong —\nBEFORE it says anything.", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s2_highlight", "x": 345, "y": 390, "text": "\"Correctness direction\"\nexists in activation space.\nYou don't need training\nto find it — it's just\nsitting there.", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#69db7c", "originalText": "\"Correctness direction\"\nexists in activation space.\nYou don't need training\nto find it — it's just\nsitting there.", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "s3_bg", "x": 680, "y": 120, "width": 320, "height": 340, "backgroundColor": "#1a1a2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#c92a2a", "strokeWidth": 2, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "opacity": 80}, {"type": "text", "id": "s3_title", "x": 690, "y": 130, "text": "WHAT DOESN'T ❌", "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#ff6b6b", "originalText": "WHAT DOESN'T ❌", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s3_body", "x": 690, "y": 165, "text": "Reasoning (GSM8K)\n\nAUROC: 0.33 → 0.64\nSame wall as No Answer\nNeeded (2025)\n\nEarly layers are BELOW\nRANDOM on reasoning\n(AUROC 0.33 at L5)\n\nModel accuracy: 3.5%\n(7/200 correct)\nExtreme class imbalance", "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#ffa8a8", "originalText": "Reasoning (GSM8K)\n\nAUROC: 0.33 → 0.64\nSame wall as No Answer\nNeeded (2025)\n\nEarly layers are BELOW\nRANDOM on reasoning\n(AUROC 0.33 at L5)\n\nModel accuracy: 3.5%\n(7/200 correct)\nExtreme class imbalance", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s3_highlight", "x": 695, "y": 370, "text": "THE REASONING GAP\nFactual: 0.87\nReasoning: 0.64\nGap: 0.23", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#ff6b6b", "originalText": "THE REASONING GAP\nFactual: 0.87\nReasoning: 0.64\nGap: 0.23", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "s4_bg", "x": 20, "y": 490, "width": 480, "height": 220, "backgroundColor": "#1a1a2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#e67700", "strokeWidth": 2, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "opacity": 80}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_title", "x": 30, "y": 500, "text": "THE BIG QUESTION 🟡", "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#ffd43b", "originalText": "THE BIG QUESTION 🟡", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s4_body", "x": 30, "y": 530, "text": "Why does the signal fail on reasoning?\n\n1. Maybe uncertainty is distributed across tokens,\n   not concentrated at the last position\n\n2. Maybe the model hasn't STARTED reasoning\n   at prefill — the computation happens during generation\n\n3. Maybe reasoning correctness is inherently nonlinear\n\n4. Maybe 3.5% accuracy = too few correct samples\n   to learn from (7 correct vs 193 wrong)", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#ffe066", "originalText": "Why does the signal fail on reasoning?\n\n1. Maybe uncertainty is distributed across tokens,\n   not concentrated at the last position\n\n2. Maybe the model hasn't STARTED reasoning\n   at prefill — the computation happens during generation\n\n3. Maybe reasoning correctness is inherently nonlinear\n\n4. Maybe 3.5% accuracy = too few correct samples\n   to learn from (7 correct vs 193 wrong)", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "s5_bg", "x": 530, "y": 490, "width": 470, "height": 220, "backgroundColor": "#1a1a2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#ae3ec9", "strokeWidth": 2, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "opacity": 80}, {"type": "text", "id": "s5_title", "x": 540, "y": 500, "text": "NEXT STEPS 🚀", "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#d0bfff", "originalText": "NEXT STEPS 🚀", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "s5_body", "x": 540, "y": 530, "text": "1. Multi-position probing\n   Extract from ALL token positions, not just last\n\n2. Base vs Aligned comparison\n   Does RLHF destroy this signal?\n   (Qwen3.5-4B vs Qwen3.5-4B-Instruct)\n\n3. Larger model\n   Does the gap shrink at 9B or 27B?\n\n4. Causal steering\n   Use the correctness direction to STEER\n   strategy selection when uncertain", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#d0bfff", "originalText": "1. Multi-position probing\n   Extract from ALL token positions, not just last\n\n2. Base vs Aligned comparison\n   Does RLHF destroy this signal?\n   (Qwen3.5-4B vs Qwen3.5-4B-Instruct)\n\n3. Larger model\n   Does the gap shrink at 9B or 27B?\n\n4. Causal steering\n   Use the correctness direction to STEER\n   strategy selection when uncertain", "autoResize": true}, {"type": "text", "id": "footer", "x": 200, "y": 730, "text": "Replication of No Answer Needed (Duan et al., 2025) | Model: Qwen3.5-4B | Code: github.com/thewildofficial/epistemic-probing-replication", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3, "strokeColor": "#495057", "originalText": "Replication of No Answer Needed (Duan et al., 2025) | Model: Qwen3.5-4B | Code: github.com/thewildofficial/epistemic-probing-replication", "autoResize": true}]}
